Text: TrainerNutritionistJeff Hope all is going great in your worldthe street is finally acknowledging ours When we last visited I promised to provide you the name and number of the guy that is training my son and who also trains Jose Cruz Jr and Ken Caminetti Having seen the good bad and ugly the training world has to offer I can say with confidence that this guy is something special His name is Blake Blackwell and can be reached at or Hope to see you at the er tonight Rockn Roll Kevin
